    </span>
    <ul class="items-center mt-3 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 sm:mt-0">
        <li>
            <a href="https://github.com/lakysme" class="mr-4 hover:underline md:mr-6 ">Other projects</a>
        </li>
    </ul>
    </div>
</footer>